on": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "陆谨为什么要重建三一门？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "既然没人好奇，也可能是有些人不敢面对这个问题，那好，我来。 为什么过去几十年不重建，偏等着和李慕玄打完一架后，就重建了？ 要知道逆生三重不是金光咒，没学明白也不会伤及自身。逆生三重的危险程度，迄今为止是仅次于丹噬的存在。 陆谨重建三一门，倘若隐瞒真相，让「后来人」继续作三重成仙的美梦，我相信会有很多青年才俊慕名前来拜师。 可这不就辜负了，他恩师左若童的苦心？ 陆谨重建三一门，若是公布真相，逆生三重不能通天，为了一个单纯的「护体」术，冒非死即伤的风险（即使是当年的左若童教，门里门外的不还是有一堆残废么），投资受益严重不成正比，还能有「后来人」吗？ 如此一来，三一门又怎么能重建的起来？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-972338e7cc1ac0d1f2fb7c26e06ed4ac_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3631343968"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2JeFsPKyktQCEAMaCTExMTcwMzA4NyDrpru5BjAAOB9ABHIKMzYzMTM0Mzk2OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1731244421.142890", "card_id": "Q_2875446278", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "赵露思和刘宇宁主演的《珠帘玉幕》开播，如何评价？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-13f2adea2a09fe542b8c41701b206974_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2875446278"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2JeFsPKyktQCEAMaCTExMTU1MTcxMiDBipa5BjAAOBtABXIKMjg3NTQ0NjI3OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1"