erpt_area": {"text": "举个例子，高加米拉战役，亚帝四万集中在阿贝拉附近。然后大流士难道就看着亚帝先摆好阵仗吗？大流士排出几万人包围亚帝的队伍？就算避开夜战，亚帝中午才起来，我去骚扰一下怎么的，慢慢的你不就越投越多。然而事实上难道要等亚帝摆好阵型再打吗？然后一个下午的决战，被 ko。怎么看起来就像是约架？如果是淞沪会战，难道鬼子会等国军摆好阵仗吗？然而事实是不断的打击对方防线，持续几个月而不是高加米拉才一个下午。是不是我理解有什么问题？我在举一个例子，莫西之战，蒙古要去和贝拉决战，如果不约又如何？我兵分几路…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a48fa96bb64ca947f67e5605eff016f3_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.1 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2481823901"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2JeFsPKyktQCEAMaCTExMTQ3Mjg3NSCb6IK5BjAAOG9AE3IKMjQ4MTgyMzkwMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1731244421.149183", "card_id": "Q_3697204667", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 WTT 法兰克福冠军赛男单决赛，林诗栋 vs 卡尔伯格，你更看好谁夺冠?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "卡尔伯格需要夺冠才能去福冈总决赛，今天晚上小莫输了有点意料之外但又好像在情理之中，不过这只是我的猜想不必当真。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb395ff6e11b343a5d0674e0589bb12d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.1 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3697204667"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2JeFsPKyktQCEAMaCTExMTcxNjE5OCDOq765BjAAOFFAFHIKMzY5NzIwNDY2N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1731244421.149456", "card_id": "Q_3668990467", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "都是重返地球，印度返回舱光洁如新，为什么中国返回舱是焦黑的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a7a647e0fb0c781ecbd3bbe26687240c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "4.1 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "n